{"word":"Elishama","slug":"elishama","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Elishama</b> <a href=\"#/H476\">H476</a> <br/> 1. Grandfather of Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=10'>Num 1:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=18'>Num 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=7&verse=48'>Num 7:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=7&verse=53'>Num 7:53</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=22'>Num 10:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=26'>1Ch 7:26</a><br/> 2. A son of David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=16'>2Sa 5:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=8'>1Ch 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=14&verse=7'>1Ch 14:7</a><br/> 3. Another son of David, elsewhere called Elishua<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=6'>1Ch 3:6</a><br/><a href='S:Elishua'>Elishua</a> <br/> 4. A descendant of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=41'>1Ch 2:41</a><br/> 5. Probably identical with a descendant of Judah above<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=25'>2Ki 25:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=41&verse=1'>Jer 41:1</a><br/> 6. A secretary to Jehoiakim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=36&verse=12'>Jer 36:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=36&verse=21'>Jer 36:21</a><br/> 7. A priest sent by Jehoshaphat to teach the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=8'>2Ch 17:8</a>"}]}